

For ubuntu Quartus requires libpng12
===
cd /tmp
wget https://netactuate.dl.sourceforge.net/project/libpng/libpng12/1.2.59/libpng-1.2.59.tar.gz
cd /tmp/libpng-1.2.59
./configure --prefix=/usr/local
make
sudo make install
sudo ldconfig


In ubuntu Quartus silent is hanging on installation steps so I am using debian:stretch
===